# NOTE: the rehearsal TLS-shim CA (infra/rehearsal/tls-shim/ca/*.crt/.key) is a
# DELIBERATELY COMMITTED THROWAWAY — it only signs *.localstack.test on an
# un-routed private net and is trusted only inside the rehearsal. See
# infra/rehearsal/tls-shim/README.md. It is NOT ignored so a fresh checkout can
# build template 9001 and render the app user-data without regenerating certs.

# Rendered cloud-init artifacts (generated from *.template by render-user-data.sh)
infra/rehearsal/proxmox/cloud-init/*.rendered.yaml
